nodes.title: Note+ (mtb)
widgets_values:
##If using for LONGANIM, the 'directory' field must be **/fstmp/ZZ**, as that is the string it is looking to replace.
##Otherwise, use a folder that contains the list of frames.
##To extract frames from video:
# `ffmpeg -y -loglevel warning -i INPUT.mp4 -r 24/1 OUTDIR/%09d.png` - 24 = FPS - Use # OUTDIR in the 'directory' field -

#FILENAME: [./ASSETS/UTIL\_MAKE\_CN.json]
###### DESC: Uses existing frames to create a video if a CN Copy of the original 'longanim' version. Creates ControlNet preprocessed videos of a specific video for use in **'1\_anim.json'**. `controlnets.json' might be a better option'. MUST BE EXPRTED AS **'1\_prep\_api.json'** TO WORK.
